---
import Button from '../components/shared/Button.astro';
import Container from '../components/shared/Container.astro';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Welcome to Compass Group">
	<main class="flex flex-col gap-y-20 md:gap-y-32 overflow-hidden">
        <section class="relative pt-32 lg:pt-48">
            <Container>
                <h2 class="pb-4 text-4xl text-center">Owning a Business</h2>
                <h3 class="pb-10 text-base text-center">DO ANY OF THESE RESONATE WITH YOU?</h3>
                <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
                    <div class="p-5 sm:p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-3xl border border-box-border bg-box-bg shadow-lg shadow-box-shadow relative overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 relative text-center">
                            <h4 class="pb-4 text-2xl">Overwhelmed?</h4>
                            <p>Are you feeling overwhelmed in the day to day demands? Too much time working in your business and not on it?</p>
                        </div>
                        <span class="absolute w-32 aspect-square -bottom-16 -right-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-full"></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-5 sm:p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-3xl border border-box-border bg-box-bg shadow-lg shadow-box-shadow relative overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 relative text-center">
                            <h4 class="pb-4 text-2xl">Anxious?</h4>
                            <p>Are you feeling anxious about cash flow? Expenses out of control? Hiring the wrong people?</p>
                        </div>
                        <span class="absolute w-32 aspect-square -bottom-16 -right-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-full"></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-5 sm:p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-3xl border border-box-border bg-box-bg shadow-lg shadow-box-shadow relative overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 relative text-center">
                            <h4 class="pb-4 text-2xl">Stuck?</h4>
                            <p>Are you feeling like your business is stuck and youâ€™re at a loss what to do next? Not sure how to take your business to the next level?</p>
                        </div>
                        <span class="absolute w-32 aspect-square -bottom-16 -right-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-full"></span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </Container>
            <Container className="mt-8 text-center">
                <div>
                    <Button variant={"primary"} className={"min-w-max"}>
                        <span class="hidden sm:flex relative z-[5]">
                            Book Your Free Discovery Call
                        </span>
                    </Button>
                </div>
            </Container>
        </section>
	</main>
</Layout>
